data.description: Fabulous 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath, two story home with numerous upgrades. Crown molding through out, designer paint, custom closets, oversized patio, solar screens, alarm system, profession dog run, 42'' cabinets, kitchen under mount lights, surround sound wiring, and customized garage. This house is a must see. Absolutely won't disappoint, extremely clean!! Featured by The Houston Chronicle.
